'''罗纳德·里根总统图书馆及公共事务中心'''（{{lang-en|Ronald Reagan Presidential Library and Center for Public Affairs}}）是美国第40任总统[[罗纳德·威尔逊·里根|罗纳德·威尔逊·里根]]的[[总统图书馆|总统图书馆]]及其最終的長眠地。由{{tsl|en|Hugh Stubb
ins|休·斯塔宾斯}}及联营公司设计，图书馆位于[[加州|加州]][[西米谷|西米谷]]，[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]市中心西北约40英里（64公里）、{{tsl|en|Chatsworth, Los Angeles, California|查茨沃斯}}以西约15英里（24公里）。罗纳德·里根总统图书馆是13个总统图书馆中最大的一个。<ref name=Hufbauer>{{cite journal |last=Hufbauer |first=Benjamin |title=The Ronald Reagan Presidential Library and Museum. Simi Valley, Calif. http://www.reaganlibrary.com |journal={{tsl|en|Journal of American History|}} |date=December 1, 2008 |volume=95 |issue=3 |pages=786–92 |doi=10.2307/27694381 |url=http://jah.oxfordjournals.org/content/95/3/786 |accessdate=February 23, 2013 |archive-date=2016-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107211641/http://jah.oxfordjournals.org/content/95/3/786 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.townandcountrymag.com/society/politics/news/a6825/obama-presidential-library/ |title=How Will the Obama Presidential Library Stack Up? |last=Lopez |first=Natalina |date=July 1, 2016 |website=Town and Country Magazine |publisher=Hearst Communications, Inc. |access-date=March 3, 2017 |quote=Perched on a hillside in Simi Valley, California, the Reagan Library wins the prize for being the largest of the presidential libraries. |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125194533/https://www.townandcountrymag.com/society/politics/news/a6825/obama-presidential-library/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

